node.text:
Savage over average💯 

So many people think if you workout it’s only to look good but not enough people talk about the feeling you get during and after a good workout! It feels so good to accomplish something that seems so hard in the moment. You learn a lot about yourself when you push yourself to the next level. 

If you see this post this is your sign to crush your fitness goals and get after it! Remember everyone starts somewhere and I strongly encourage you to get out of your comfort zone! You won’t regret it!
